tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE RealTimeDataIngestion (
  data_feed_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data_feed_name VARCHAR(255),
  data_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  data_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE real_time_streaming_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data_feed VARCHAR(255),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE sas_analytics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data_analysis VARCHAR(255),
  live_feed BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE sas_live_data_feeds (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data_source VARCHAR(255),
  data_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  data_value DOUBLE
)

CREATE TABLE analytics_results (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  result_info TEXT,
  result_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  result_score INT
)

CREATE TABLE data_ingestion_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  log_message TEXT,
  log_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE real_time_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data TIMESTAMP,
  value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE analytics_results (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  result_data VARCHAR(255),
  result_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE live_data_feeds (
  feed_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  feed_name VARCHAR(100),
  feed_data JSON
)

CREATE TABLE sas_analytics (
  analytics_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  analytics_tool VARCHAR(50),
  analytics_date TIMESTAMP
)
